---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Us"
  description="TopNice aggregates the most innovative physical products from Kickstarter and Indiegogo. Discover robots, gadgets, hardware, and more."
  lang="en"
>
  <section class="page-content">
    <h1>About TopNice</h1>
    <p>TopNice is a product discovery platform that aggregates crowdfunding projects from <strong>Kickstarter</strong> and <strong>Indiegogo</strong>, updated on daily basis.</p>
    <p>We focus exclusively on physical products — robots, gadgets, hardware, 3D printers, camera gear, toys, and tabletop games. Our mission is to help backers discover the most exciting new hardware before it hits the market.</p>
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p>Project data includes funding progress, backer counts, categories, creator information, and direct links to the original campaign pages.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For inquiries, feedback, or partnership opportunities, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@topnice.com">hello@topnice.com</a>.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 120px 48px 80px;
  }
  .page-content h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  .page-content h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .page-content p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .page-content a {
    color: #f97316;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-content { padding: 100px 20px 60px; }
    .page-content h1 { font-size: 28px; }
  }
</style>
